            log.info('Password reset for user "%s" IP-address: %s', form['username'], ip_Address)
            return redirect(form['reset_link'])
```

Here, the code redirects to the URL provided in the'reset_link' form field without checking its validity. An attacker can manipulate this field to include a malicious URL, which can lead to SSRF attacks.
